Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.35,0:00:05.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,流行性？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.60,0:00:07.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,耳下腺炎
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.39,0:00:10.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,称作  流行性耳下腺炎
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.58,0:00:13.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是说…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.49,0:00:17.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是常说的多福感冒
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.63,0:00:19.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,需要休养一个星期
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.31,0:00:22.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,学校呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.69,0:00:23.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能去
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.82,0:00:24.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打针呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.95,0:00:25.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要打
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.61,0:02:07.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,The spear is very break and hard,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.58,0:02:09.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,and it is large and long,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.86,0:02:11.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Jurinsa thows it,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.21,0:02:14.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yahunture grabs it,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.61,0:02:16.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,As she pressing it against him.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.22,0:02:19.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,But she had never fought...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.67,0:02:24.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到学美出院为止  学生会就只剩我和芽生了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.97,0:02:33.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜托你整理一下
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.86,0:02:41.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个…这些都要…整理啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.20,0:02:47.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没什么…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.33,0:03:31.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样说来  还从没跟小芽单独说过话呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.66,0:03:38.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,努力和小芽愉快地聊聊天
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.09,0:03:41.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后回家的时候再一起吃个饭
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.09,0:03:44.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.36,0:03:53.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我先告辞了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.24,0:04:02.48,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,晾衣竿  卖晾衣竿了～
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.73,0:04:03.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,绝对没法办到
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.19,0:04:08.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总觉得学美一不在就没人起头聊天了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.28,0:04:11.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是不是神经太过紧绷了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.95,0:04:13.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听我说  蜜柑
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.50,0:04:16.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很不好意思  明天垒球部还有体能训练
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.76,0:04:18.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在不是跟你谈这些的时候…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.73,0:04:20.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们是朋友吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.41,0:04:25.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的  只要适当地配合一下她的话题不就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.50,0:04:26.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎样的话题才算？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.40,0:04:29.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,昨天看过的电视之类的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.86,0:04:32.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小芽好像不看电视的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.53,0:04:34.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最近听过的CD呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.68,0:04:38.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她好像喜欢听古典的  我一点都不懂啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.39,0:04:42.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样一来她会笑话我的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.42,0:04:46.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊呀  找人帮忙的话去找小桃啊  去找小桃
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.78,0:04:49.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我已经叫她了呀
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.19,0:05:02.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你应该知道小芽就是这性格  跟她妥协一下也没问题吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.75,0:05:04.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是呀～
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.58,0:05:08.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她才刚进的学生会  心里比你还没底呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.19,0:05:10.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好好对人家哦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.73,0:05:12.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是呀～
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.19,0:05:14.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐  吃饭了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.48,0:05:16.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我挂了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.50,0:05:18.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么啦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.05,0:05:20.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.42,0:05:21.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的  罗哩吧嗦的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.20,0:05:23.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了  吃饭吃饭
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.56,0:05:27.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蜜…柑…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.14,0:05:28.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.61,0:05:35.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.60,0:06:00.35,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（关门  请明天再来）
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.19,0:06:06.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思  我今天有事不能去了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.15,0:06:09.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊…啊…是这样吗…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.03,0:06:10.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再见
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.91,0:06:19.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  跟她交上朋友了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.51,0:06:20.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,问到什么隐私了吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.90,0:06:22.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们都在聊些什么
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.40,0:06:25.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,学园祭宣传时的CG真的是卫藤同学做的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.58,0:06:26.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也想知道
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.28,0:06:27.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂…喂
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.18,0:06:29.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的很厉害呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.84,0:06:33.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老实说  跟她单独在一起一定很吃力吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.98,0:06:35.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才没有…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.71,0:06:43.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才没有…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.34,0:06:46.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…那样呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.96,0:06:57.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她心里比你还没底呢  好好对人家哦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.59,0:07:00.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也想要好好对她的呀
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.29,0:07:02.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.75,0:07:04.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊…没事
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.94,0:07:07.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,邮件？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.94,0:07:11.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.88,0:07:15.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然  虽然用嘴说不上来
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.61,0:07:19.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要写信  能有个开端的话  肯定能跟她拉近距离
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.23,0:07:20.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定能成为好朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.80,0:07:22.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一定要踏出第一步
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.18,0:07:28.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小  小芽…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.71,0:07:33.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  那个  还真巧呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.75,0:07:34.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.65,0:07:36.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你常来这里吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.34,0:07:36.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从没来过
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.23,0:07:37.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.33,0:07:45.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,踏出第一步  踏出第一步
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.91,0:07:46.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,信
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.73,0:07:48.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你要写信吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.54,0:07:50.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯…嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.86,0:07:51.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,写给谁？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.88,0:07:54.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那…那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.36,0:08:01.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给  给学美写…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.47,0:08:03.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是么
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.00,0:08:04.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也是
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.47,0:08:06.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我先走了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.31,0:08:52.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,光香  早上了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.74,0:08:53.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快起床
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.28,0:09:03.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真不想去学校啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.14,0:09:07.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的  要迟到的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.95,0:09:11.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妈妈  我今天…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.99,0:09:15.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  对了对了  有你的信哦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.06,0:09:16.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,信？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.50,0:09:21.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有邮戳  应该是直接放在邮箱里的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.05,0:09:22.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.68,0:09:27.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天就吃面包吧  没多少时间了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.80,0:09:32.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我出门了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.83,0:09:33.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一下  光香
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.66,0:09:36.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打电话给上原同学商量了一下
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.03,0:09:39.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她建议我要不要写写信看
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.50,0:09:42.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我就写了这封信
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.58,0:09:47.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…其实我并不擅长跟人交谈
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.31,0:09:52.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但我也不是不想交朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.28,0:09:57.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然不知道该怎么写
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.23,0:09:59.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  蜜柑
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.63,0:10:01.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你为什么昨天没接电话…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.98,0:10:04.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然不知道该怎么写
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.73,0:10:13.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,稻森同学你既温柔  又开朗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.40,0:10:17.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想要是能与你自由地交谈该多好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.18,0:10:20.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,学生会  要一起加油哦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.23,0:10:56.20,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「给稻森同学  卫藤芽生」
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.29,0:11:04.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有一部分同学对学园祭是否会延期有所疑问呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.32,0:11:10.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有这回事哦  学园祭的准备活动才刚刚开始呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.95,0:11:12.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不会延期么
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.08,0:11:18.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,学生会还有蜜柑和小芽在  大概没问题的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.07,0:11:21.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对了小桃
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.46,0:11:21.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.60,0:11:25.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…你们这身衣服在哪里买的？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.90,0:11:29.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,网上…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.84,0:11:32.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,主题？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.10,0:11:36.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不错  在上次的学生总会上
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.80,0:11:40.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们所要展现的学园祭的大致概念  我们已经能了解
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.19,0:11:45.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是  具体来说\N你们到底想要得到什么效果  该如何行动
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.21,0:11:51.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不事先定好方针的话  或许也会和去年一样搞出个不知所谓的学园祭来
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.21,0:11:53.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来如此
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.10,0:11:57.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  「生机勃勃  令人兴奋」这样的不行吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.12,0:12:01.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…不  应该再具体一点吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.22,0:12:05.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是说在体制上可以被承认的像样点的说法吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.01,0:12:11.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对于全权交与学生负责的学园祭  有些老师也存在着不安吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.73,0:12:12.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是这样吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.39,0:12:15.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶？是那样吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.43,0:12:21.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,圣樱可是历史悠久  有优良传统的学园哦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.78,0:12:25.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,存在对天宫同学的做法不理解的教师  也并不稀奇
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.50,0:12:29.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真过分——！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.82,0:12:32.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下岛这个叛徒！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.35,0:12:33.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可饶恕！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.07,0:12:38.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我认为下岛老师是反对他们的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.56,0:12:39.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.53,0:12:43.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以  要想一个让我们提出他们反对方接受的主题
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.63,0:12:45.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是…是那样的吗  下岛？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.19,0:12:48.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算是吧…总之
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.99,0:12:52.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,先不管那回事  就我刚才说的主题是绝对需要的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.05,0:12:55.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唔…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.30,0:12:59.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们自己也要给自己定个指标
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.23,0:13:03.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,借这个机会认真的考虑一下也并不坏  是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.11,0:13:04.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,确实
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.31,0:13:07.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从天宫出院后开始算起
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.69,0:13:09.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总之…给你们一个星期时间吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.93,0:13:11.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  这差不多能接受
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.25,0:13:13.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个…下岛
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.20,0:13:14.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.19,0:13:17.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们两个人讨论不行吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.68,0:13:18.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.15,0:13:21.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在…学美…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.33,0:13:28.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在学美回来之前  我们两个人开始考虑主题不行吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.79,0:13:40.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的  老师他毕竟也是老师啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.91,0:13:44.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听取两个人想出来的主题的话  也太…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.03,0:13:48.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家觉得我们是「随意想出」的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.88,0:13:50.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是「随意想出」的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.97,0:13:53.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为是两个人尝试想出的主题哦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.67,0:13:55.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我和小芽两个人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.75,0:14:02.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那样的…所以才说是「随意想出」的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.03,0:14:06.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一起努力吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.44,0:14:08.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小芽
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.55,0:14:15.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.26,0:14:25.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没什么感觉啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.50,0:14:29.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然说哪一个作为主题都不错…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.93,0:14:35.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么会这样欠缺灵感呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.44,0:14:39.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大概  这些都太追求华丽反而过于笼统了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.11,0:14:43.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无法令人觉得「生机勃勃  令人兴奋」了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.43,0:14:44.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.97,0:14:50.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.61,0:14:50.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.33,0:14:51.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.30,0:14:56.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂喂
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.56,0:14:58.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样的话在比赛中可是赢不了的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.81,0:14:59.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还剩三圈
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.00,0:15:00.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拿出气势来…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.81,0:15:05.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如何？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.62,0:15:07.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感…感觉好像要想出什么来了…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.77,0:15:10.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那  再跑一圈吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.52,0:15:28.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,FIGHT ON  FIGHT ON…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.86,0:15:31.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们还是…按照我们自己的方法来考虑吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.19,0:15:33.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,赞…赞成…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.80,0:15:34.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呜…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.41,0:15:37.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咽下去了…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.65,0:15:39.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能忍住不吐出来真是太好了…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.60,0:15:45.12,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（学美出院日！）
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.66,0:16:19.86,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（风格与用语要统一  避开抽象以及暧昧的表现）
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.07,0:17:37.71,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（今天要定下来！）
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.50,0:17:45.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然还是不好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.25,0:17:47.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没关系没关系
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.05,0:17:48.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.23,0:17:57.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘘——
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.53,0:18:01.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算了  这样也好
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.84,0:18:06.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,肚子…饿了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.80,0:18:09.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这么乱来的话饭会烧糊的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.58,0:18:11.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这…这样才不会烧糊呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.72,0:18:15.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我吃饱了～
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.79,0:18:20.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊～好饱好饱
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.31,0:18:31.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.15,0:18:33.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯…？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.78,0:18:36.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不给家里打个电话说一声行吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.59,0:18:39.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,家里的人不担心吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.66,0:18:43.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.43,0:18:50.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小芽
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.90,0:18:51.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯…？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.98,0:18:55.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样躺着的话  就能更好地看星星了哟
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.27,0:20:17.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上好～
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.85,0:20:22.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上好～
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.87,0:20:31.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上好～
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.37,0:20:34.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天宫学美  出院了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.97,0:20:37.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我听同学说你们在…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.63,0:20:43.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀呀  睡着了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.74,0:21:01.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.74,0:21:04.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,学美？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.26,0:21:11.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那…那个
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.02,0:21:13.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个文件是…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.34,0:21:14.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.84,0:21:18.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太棒了～
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.91,0:21:19.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要抱着我！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.48,0:21:24.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和小芽成为朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.54,0:21:27.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后  又似乎成为了亲密的伙伴
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.89,0:21:32.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,通过学园祭  应该会和更多的人结成伙伴吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.20,0:21:36.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是那么想的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.80,0:21:39.10,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（从朋友到伙伴）
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.86,0:21:46.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀哎呀
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.14,0:22:00.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好困
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.32,0:23:47.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第六话  『桂糖甜甜圈·幸福』
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.32,0:23:47.39,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（注：シュガーレイズド是某家专门生产甜甜圈的公司的产品名）
